#

Teriyaki Burger

25 min
$15
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

BurgerGrilledQuick Meal

Description

A juicy burger topped with a sweet and savory teriyaki sauce and fresh pineapple, delivering a delightful taste of the tropics.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • teriyaki sauce: 1/4 cup
  • burger buns: 4
  • pineapple slices: 4
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • sliced tomatoes: 1
  • sliced onions: 1/2
  • cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • vegetable oil: 1 tbsp
